Product Description: Spine Referencing Instrumentation, Spinous Process Clamp, Tall  When used with a Medtronic StealthStation Navigation System, the Spine Referencing fixation devices are intended to provide rigid attachment between patient and patient reference frame for the duration of the surgery.
